				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "One of the waveservants, singing on the funeral. \r\nWon't talk to a player during the funeral, won't tell much after that too.\r\n\r\nAfter the Beastmaster quest is completed, the ceremony is no longer going on, so they have a different dialog then."
				}
			}
		}
	}
